tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE bioreactor_monitoring (
    bioreactor_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    temperature FLOAT,
    pH FLOAT,
    oxygen_level FLOAT,
    agitation_speed INT,
    enzyme_production BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE bioreactors (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    reactor_name STRING,
    temperature FLOAT,
    ph_level FLOAT,
    volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE fermentation_logs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    bioreactor_id UUID REFERENCES bioreactors(id),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    glucose_concentration FLOAT,
    ethanol_concentration FLOAT,
    oxygen_level FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE enzyme_production (
    production_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    bioreactor_id UUID REFERENCES bioreactors(id),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    enzyme_type STRING,
    enzyme_yield FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Bioreactor_monitoring (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    temperature DECIMAL,
    pressure DECIMAL,
    pH DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Enzyme_production (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    enzyme_name VARCHAR(50),
    production_date DATE,
    quantity INT
)

CREATE TABLE Fermentation (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    fermentation_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Control_system (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    system_name VARCHAR(50),
    status BOOLEAN,
    mode VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE bioreactor_settings (
    bioreactor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    temperature FLOAT,
    pressure FLOAT,
    agitation_speed FLOAT
)
